{
  "stem": "7282.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, like-- she had a cousin, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Hailey.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he had been working at Jack [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Parsland's ?] factory as a shipper there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was a cutter.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So he got me the job.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he got me the job right away because, you see, you couldn't get into Canada if you haven't got a job.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he got me the job, and I couldn't get out from Poland.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the job been waiting.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, they had been waiting-- he was keeping it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They didn't want to wait so long.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But they liked him very much.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they kept the place for me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I got here, I went right away to the job and start to work there, or what.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I had already a job.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my, my wife, she hadn't got a job there, or what.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when I used to come back home from work in the evening, she used to cry the whole evening and the whole night for a month-- more than a month.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, you see, it-- in my case, it was already the third time-- one from Kiev to Ostrog, from Ostrog to Poland, from Poland here.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Yeah, and it didn't take a month.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It takes years.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So in the meantime, I got established.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I got to sell everything to break everything, and to start here from scratch.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So it, it was very bad.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I mean, not that I'm complaining.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I mean, when we got here, I mean, we lived with, with her sister in the beginning.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She took us in, or what.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But I had a job.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So I made $0.80 an hour.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I made-- during the week, I made $20 or $25 a week.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
